spub.org/file/5-1250337x171_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。若存在<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250337x172_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>以及<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250337x173_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的仿射区间<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250337x174_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>满足：</p><disp-formula id="scirp.15366-formula3179"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250337x175_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>则<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250337x176_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula></p><p>证明：记<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250337x177_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，由于<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250337x178_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>内部非空所以取<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250337x179_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，使得<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250337x180_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250337x181_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，并且<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250337x182_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>定义如下两个函数：</p><disp-formula id="scirp.15366-formula3180"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250337x183_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><disp-formula id="scirp.15366-formula3181"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-1250337x184_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula